<content>1 Administration

1.1 Home Page

* the central page (release November 2010) is WebHomeVistor, Normally it is viewed at the &lt;a href="/"&gt;root of the domain&lt;/a&gt;. It can be [viewed embedded&gt;Main.WebHomeVistor], &lt;a href="/xwiki/bin/edit/Main/WebHomeVistor"&gt;edited&lt;/a&gt; or one can view its &lt;a href="/xwiki/bin/view/Main/WebHomeVistor?viewer=history"&gt;history&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href="/xwiki/bin/view/Main/WebHomeVistor?viewer=attachments"&gt;attachments&lt;/a&gt;. The tradition has been, thus far, to include all attachments in one zip containing one directory called images with files inside.
* the older home page is still visible &lt;a href="/xwiki/bin/view/Main/WebHome?param=useless"&gt;view&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="/xwiki/bin/view/Main/WebHome?viewer=history"&gt;history&lt;/a&gt;

