1.1 Restart Scripts
*Only use these if you know what you are doing and you let everyone know you are restarting.*
* *Current*: Restart XWiki [nicely&gt;http://current.dev.curriki.org/restart/restart.shtml], check the [tail of the log&gt;http://current.dev.curriki.org/restart/logtail.shtml], or restart it [harshly&gt;http://current.dev.curriki.org/restart/restart-9.shtml].
** sources are in subversion for [appserv's restart scripts&gt;http://svn.curriki.org/configs/dev/appservbin] and and [apache's restart scripts&gt;http://svn.curriki.org/configs/dev/apache-htdocs-restart]

* [ Restart Beta&gt;http://beta.curriki.org/restart/restart.shtml]
* [ Restart Next&gt;http://next.dev.curriki.org/restart/restart.shtml]


